<div class="container text-center mainhead">
  <div class="row">
     <h1> CHOOSE OR CREATE YOUR BURGERS! <br>
       <small class="text"> Wich one(s) of this delicious burgers are you going to devour!!!</small>
     </h1>
  </div>
